Sony,Lifelog,is,an,application,for,wearables,that,tracks,and,records,various,data,from,the,user,such,as,health,information,fitness,information,and,goal,tracking,The,Sony,Lifelog,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Lifelog,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,managing,users,retrieving,activity,information,and,accessing,location,data